      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.2LjlJwvdgzejPYV5]{Brief Mutagen}</p>\n<p>You have developed a special metamorphosis injection that can physically transform a limb into an oversized pincer claw. Once per day per 4 biohacker levels, as a standard action, you can use your custom microlab to target a willing ally with a special biohack that endows them with an unarmed strike for 1 round per biohacker level. This unarmed strike deals lethal damage, doesn’t count as archaic, threatens squares, and has the grapple special property (Starfinder Armory 28). The target also adds 1-1/2 × their level to the damage it deals.</p>\n<p><em>Damage calculation is already set to account the additional damage of 1/2 × their character level, beyond the damage provided by their normal Weapon Specialization damage.</em></p>"
